column1: The experiments 1-9 are the different density value simulations
and the experiments 10-18 are the different total mass value simulations.
1-9 all run with box size 1000 and then amount of heavy nuclei values 600-1400 in steps of 100.
10-18 run with the same heavy nucleus values 600-1400 in steps of 100
but with corresponding box sizes to keep the density of heavy nuclei constant.
